{
  "_comment": [
    "MapCoordinates.json — Single source of truth for ride map positions.",
    "",
    "Fields per entry:",
    "  id        — StableID matching RideSeeder: '{Park.rawValue}|{land}|{name}'",
    "  rideName  — Display name shown in annotation labels and accessibility strings.",
    "  land      — Canonical land name; must match a value in Park.lands.",
    "  parkId    — Backend park identifier (Park.backendId).",
    "  lat / lon — GPS coordinate of the ride entrance / main building.",
    "  category  — Ride type hint for marker icon selection.",
    "  entityId  — ThemeParks.wiki v1 entity UUID for this attraction.",
    "              null = not yet verified from the API.",
    "              Obtain verified IDs by fetching:",
    "                GET https://api.themeparks.wiki/v1/entity/{park.themeparksEntityId}/live",
    "              and matching each child by name, then recording its 'id' field here.",
    "              MapCoordinateService.validate() logs every null entityId at launch.",
    "",
    "Coverage contract:",
    "  Every MasterAttraction with shouldAppearOnMap == true (mapPriority != nil)",
    "  must have exactly one entry here. Attractions with mapPriority == nil",
    "  (character meets, non-map shows) must NOT have entries here.",
    "  mapPriority drives whether a pin is expected; this file provides the GPS.",
    "",
    "Coordinate sources:",
    "  Coordinates are based on satellite imagery and ThemeParks.wiki entity data.",
    "  Park bounds used for validation:",
    "    Magic Kingdom       28.4160–28.4230 N,  81.5865–81.5750 W",
    "    EPCOT               28.3670–28.3765 N,  81.5545–81.5450 W",
    "    Hollywood Studios   28.3525–28.3610 N,  81.5650–81.5560 W",
    "    Animal Kingdom      28.3530–28.3630 N,  81.5945–81.5860 W",
    "    Disneyland          33.8090–33.8165 N, 117.9240–117.9160 W",
    "    California Adventure 33.8040–33.8095 N, 117.9240–117.9160 W"
  ],
